<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE reference PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Reference//EN" "reference.dtd">
<reference id="api_onconnectionstatechanged">
    <title><ph keyref="onConnectionStateChanged"></ph></title>
    <shortdesc id="short">网络连接状态已改变回调。</shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="onConnectionStateChanged" />
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody><section id="prototype">
        <title>原型</title>
        <p conref="../conref/conref_rtc_api.dita#apidef/onConnectionStateChanged"/>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <title>详细描述</title>
            <dl>
                <dlentry outputclass="since">
                    <dt>自从</dt>
                    <dd>v2.3.2</dd>
                </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>该回调在网络连接状态发生改变的时候触发，并告知用户当前的网络连接状态和引起网络状态改变的原因。</p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>参数</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>state</pt>
                    <pd>当前网络连接状态。详见 <xref keyref="CONNECTION_STATE_TYPE"></xref>。</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>reason</pt>
                    <pd>引起当前网络连接状态改变的原因。详见 <xref keyref="CONNECTION_CHANGED_REASON_TYPE"></xref>。</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
</refbody>
</reference>
